rges when you book through .\",\"What is Abdominal Pain?\",\"Abdominal pain is common and often minor. Severe abdominal pain must be attended to swiftly. People who are very old or very young and those human immunodeficiency virus (HIV) infection or are taking drugs that suppress the immune system are affected.\"]','2020-06-30 07:16:05','2020-06-30 07:16:05'),(129,'1','[\"How can I book an appointment with a doctor for Arm Artery Disease in ?\",\"to book an appointment with top doctors for Arm Artery Disease in Lahore. Or, you can also call at 0345-0435621 from 9AM to 11PM to book your appointment.\",\"What is the fee range of top doctors for Arm Artery Disease in ?\",\"The fee for top doctors for Arm Artery Disease in Lahore ranges from 2000 to 2550. You will pay at the reception when you visit the doctor.\",\"Are there any additional charges to book an appointment with doctors for Arm Artery Disease in Lahore through ?\",\"There are no additional charges when you book through .\"]','2020-06-30 07:18:04','2020-06-30 07:18:04'),(130,'1','[\"How can I book an appointment with a doctor for Back Pain in ?\",\"to book an appointment with top doctors for Back Pain in Lahore. Or, you can also call at 0345-0435621 from 9AM to 11PM to book your appointment.\",\"What is the fee range of top doctors for Back Pain in Lahore?\",\"The fee for top doctors for Back Pain in Lahore ranges from 500 to 3500. You will pay at the reception when you visit the doctor.\",\"Are there any additional charges to book an appointment with doctors for Back Pain in Lahore through ?\",\"There are no additional charges when you book through .\"]','2020-06-30 07:21:16','2020-06-30 07:21:16'),(131,'1','[\"How can I book an appointment with a doctor performing Foreign Body Impaction in ?\",\"to book an appointment with top doctors performing Foreign Body Impaction in Lahore. Or, you can also call at 0345-0435621 from 9AM to 11PM to book your appointment.\",\"What is the fee range of top doctors perform